The educational video explains how ChatGPT, a language model, functions by modeling sequences of words, characters or tokens. Andrej gives the AI a beginning sequence, and it completes the sequence with an outcome. The AI generates answers based on the sequence and can deliver several different responses to the same prompt, showing its probabilistic nature. There are numerous prompts that can be given to ChatGPT, and it generates creative and diverse responses, often with a touch of humor.